  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `useAiSummary.ts:285` — record the literal playbook name string + URL pattern.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `DocumentEmailWizard.tsx:628` — same.</step>
    <step order="3">Map each literal name → stable code via spec §1.7.3 codes table.</step>
    <step order="4">Refactor `useAiSummary.ts:285`: change fetch URL from `/api/ai/playbooks/by-name/{name}` to `/api/ai/playbooks/by-id/{id}`; replace literal name with code constant.</step>
    <step order="5">Refactor `DocumentEmailWizard.tsx:628`: same pattern.</step>
    <step order="6">Add error-handling for ProblemDetails 404 shape (from task 011): show user-friendly "Playbook unavailable" message instead of raw error.</step>
    <step order="7">Update Vitest unit tests for both files — mock fetch returns `/by-code/` response; assert URL pattern.</step>
    <step order="8">Build each affected solution: `cd src/client/code-pages/AnalysisWorkspace && npm install --legacy-peer-deps --no-audit --no-fund && npm run build` ; similarly for SpaarkeAi.</step>
    <step order="9">Run UI smoke test per `<ui-tests>` section: console-error free, dark-mode toggle works, click-summary triggers correct `/by-code/` URL (verify via network tab observation in test).</step>
    <step order="10">Measure publish artifacts — code-page bundle size and SpaarkeAi bundle size; report deltas (NFR-01 is BFF-only but bundle hygiene matters).</step>
    <step order="11">Run code-review + adr-check (Step 9.5 FULL gates).</step>
    <step order="12">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 021 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

