    <test type="console-error">UI surfaces (AnalysisWorkspace code-page + SpaarkeAi DocumentEmailWizard) must render with zero console errors after migration.</test>
    <test type="dark-mode">Per ADR-021, verify dark-mode toggle still works on both affected surfaces — no regressions in theming or token usage.</test>
    <test type="interaction-smoke">Manually trigger the summary flow (or simulate via Playwright) and verify the network request URL is `/api/ai/playbooks/by-id/{id}` and the response is consumed without error.</test>
  </ui-tests>

